<Layout title="How to Rank in Perplexity — UK Guide | Rank4AI" description="How to get your business cited by Perplexity. Perplexity SEO guide for UK businesses from Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">How to Rank in Perplexity</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Perplexity is a real-time open web crawler that explicitly cites its sources. Unlike ChatGPT, you can see exactly where Perplexity gets its information — and whether your business is one of those sources.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Sites with a domain authority of 40+ are sourced 6x more frequently. The first 150 words of your content matter most for extraction. High-trust, well-structured, indexed content performs best.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What Perplexity Looks For</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Clear, structured answers</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Perplexity extracts and cites content that directly answers questions. Structure your pages around clear questions and clear answers.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Independent sources</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Perplexity cross-references multiple sources. Being mentioned consistently across directories, publications and review platforms increases citation likelihood.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Freshness</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Perplexity crawls in real-time. Recently updated content with clear dates is prioritised over stale pages.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Entity clarity</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Clear entity definition and multiple independent sources describing the business consistently. One voice is weak. Many consistent voices are strong.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
